									<p class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-info-prep entry-info-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/category/food/" title="View all posts in Food" rel="category tag">Food</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/category/food/recipes/" title="View all posts in Recipes" rel="category tag">Recipes</a>					</p>
