									<p class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-info-prep entry-info-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/category/food/" title="View all posts in Food" rel="category tag">Food</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/category/food/recipes/" title="View all posts in Recipes" rel="category tag">Recipes</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a>					</p>
													<p class="tag-links">
						<span class="entry-info-prep entry-info-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/basil/" rel="tag">Basil</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/main-meal/" rel="tag">Main Meal</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/miso/" rel="tag">Miso</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/pasta/" rel="tag">Pasta</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/pesto/" rel="tag">Pesto</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/vegan/" rel="tag">Vegan</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/vegetarian/" rel="tag">Vegetarian</a>, <a href="http://howtomakeamess.wordpress.com/tag/walnuts/" rel="tag">Walnuts</a>					</p>
